# Group Users 

## Self [/self]

### View the currently authenticated user [GET]
+ Headers
    Authorization : {JWT token}
+ Response 200(application/json)
{
  "type": "User",
  "id": 1,
  "roles": [
    {
      "type": "Role",
      "id": 1,
      "name": "admin"
    }
  ],
  "name": "testUser",
  "userName": "testUser"
}

### Update the currently authenticated user [PATCH]

## Users [/users]
+ Headers
    Authorization : {JWT token}

### Creates a new user [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    {
        "name" : "wtf",
        "userName" : "test wtf",
        "password" : "1234",
        "roles" : ["admin"]
    }
+ Response 200(application/json)
{
  "type": "User",
  "id": 4,
  "roles": [
    {
      "type": "Role",
      "id": 1,
      "name": "admin"
    }
  ],
  "name": "wtf",
  "userName": "test wtf"
}


### Views all users [GET]
+ Response 200(application/json)
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "roles": [
