## User [/users/{user_id}]
+ Parameters
    + user_id (number, required) - ID of the user in form of an integer.
    
   
### View a users information [GET]

### Update a user [PATCH]
+ Headers
    Authorization : {JWT token}

+ Response 204 (application/json)

### Reset users password [GET /users/{user_id}/reset-password]